@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #ECEFF1
skinparam classBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam classBorderColor #455A64
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
[*] --> Pending
Pending --> Completed : submit
Completed --> Delivered : reject
Delivered --> Draft : submit
Delivered : entry / log course
Draft --> Created : reject
Draft : entry / log course
Created --> Approved : process
Created : entry / log course
Created --> Completed : revert
Approved --> [*]
@enduml